## Summary
This documentation describes Amplitude's X Ads integration that imports campaign-level spend, click, and impression data as "Daily Ad Metrics" events with properties like `ad_metrics.impressions`, `ad_metrics.clicks`, and campaign identifiers, requiring X Ads Manager Admin access and manual UTM parameter setup for proper attribution tracking.

